//How to create an Array

//Syntax:
 1: Datatype [] Variable_Name=New Datatype[size];
 2: Datatype  Variable_Name=New Datatype[size]; 

// Example:

int a []=new int [6];  //length of array is declaired here i.e. 6 is the the length of an array //Array Declairation

// How to insert elements(number/string/char/boolean etc) in an array

//Syntax

Array_name(it will be variable name) [index_number]=value(type should be same as that type of declaired datatype of an array);
a [0]=10;  //array Initialisation  //index value will be now from 0 to 5 bcoz length is 6
a [4]=25;
a [3]=30;
a [1]=9;
a [2]=20;
a [5]=25;
